since it's under the central government.

1142
00:37:59,572 --> 00:38:01,811
He told them that I was diligent,

1143
00:38:01,812 --> 00:38:03,712
and even though I hadn't learned everything,

1144
00:38:04,212 --> 00:38:07,351
