1151
00:38:20,532 --> 00:38:22,061
So I thought it would be five years, but...

1152
00:38:22,062 --> 00:38:23,062
It didn't end.

1153
00:38:23,063 --> 00:38:25,261
- I was there for 20 years.
- Gosh.

1154
00:38:25,262 --> 00:38:27,401
