- "Pass."

1156
00:38:28,802 --> 00:38:31,101
During the transition from President Kim Dae Jung to Roh Moo Hyun,

1157
00:38:31,102 --> 00:38:32,672
I was the only one who wasn't replaced.

1158
00:38:33,072 --> 00:38:34,841
From President Roh Moo Hyun...

1159
