1160
00:38:36,072 --> 00:38:38,041
I was the only one who wasn't replaced again.

1161
00:38:38,042 --> 00:38:40,041
So, I think I was a bit lucky, somehow.

1162
00:38:40,042 --> 00:38:41,881
- You are such a good person, - With just skills,

1163
00:38:41,882 --> 00:38:43,052
- and diligent, so...
- it's not easy.

1164
00:38:43,282 --> 00:38:46,581
Then I would like to ask, since you went to the Blue House,

1165
00:38:46,582 --> 00:38:48,751
