1182
00:39:14,482 --> 00:39:15,951
- For the ingredients?
- For the ingredients.

1183
00:39:15,952 --> 00:39:17,281
They need to be there in person as well.

1184
00:39:17,282 --> 00:39:19,281
- Who does that?
- The food taster?

1185
00:39:19,282 --> 00:39:21,652
The food taster is part of the Security Office.

1186
00:39:22,492 --> 00:39:23,821
The Food Inspection Division...

1187
00:39:23,822 --> 00:39:26,062
