- That's nonsense.

1194
00:39:35,732 --> 00:39:37,501
That person is not qualified to be a food taster.

1195
00:39:37,502 --> 00:39:39,201
- They can't be picky.
- No.

1196
00:39:39,202 --> 00:39:40,341
