1197
00:39:40,342 --> 00:39:41,811
But they could have allergies even if they are healthy.

1198
00:39:41,812 --> 00:39:42,941
- Sure.
- Right.

1199
00:39:42,942 --> 00:39:43,981
That would be...

1200
00:39:43,982 --> 00:39:46,181
If they have allergies,

1201
00:39:46,182 --> 00:39:48,012
